question: I’m pretty sure dan said the dog stuff in his first solo liveshow after the move, and the forever home one in the first joint liveshow they did after the move.
answer:
I’m pretty sure you’re talking about the part with the infamous quote “phil is obsessed with a corgi.. or maybe it will be an ugly mongrel that we adopt”, which happened in his first solo liveshow after the move (here starting at 55:57 until 56:41).
